<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Farmer Awareness Platform</title>
    <style>
        /* Basic Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #96B6C5;
            color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1;
            padding: 5px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0%;
            right: 0%;
        }

        header h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        #cards-section {
            background-color: A7C6DA;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        section {
            padding: 40px 0;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: black;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 6px 6px 12px #bebebe, -6px -6px 12px #ffffff;
            padding: 50px;
            margin: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .card h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #2980b9;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .card p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .slider-container {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            max-width: 450px;
            height: 300px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .slider {
            display: flex;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            transition: transform 1s ease-in-out;
        }

        .slider img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: fill;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 10;
            box-shadow: 0 -4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        footer .social-links {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        footer .social-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-size: 24px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer .social-links a:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        footer .back-to-top {
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #f39c12;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #333;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        footer .back-to-top:hover {
            background-color: #f39c12;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Media Queries for Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                width: 90%;
            }

            header h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }

            section h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .card {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Farmer Awareness Platform</h2>
            <p>Your trusted source for the latest agricultural information, schemes, and innovations</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section id="cards-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Explore Agricultural Information</h2>

            <!-- Food Wastage Awareness Card -->
            <div class="card" id="food-wastage-card">
                <h3>Food Wastage in Agriculture</h3>
                <div class="slider-container">
                    <div class="slider">
                        <img src="https://timesofagriculture.in/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Food-Wastage-in-India-data.jpg"
                            alt="Food Wastage">
                    </div>
                </div><br>
                <p><b>Understand the magnitude of food wastage in agriculture and the efforts being made to reduce
                        it.</b></p>
                <p>Food wastage in agriculture is a significant issue in India, with nearly 40% of produce lost annually
                    due to inadequate storage, transportation, and infrastructure. This wastage is primarily seen in
                    perishable items like fruits and vegetables. Poor cold chain facilities and post-harvest handling
                    contribute heavily to the losses. Initiatives like the National Mission on Food Processing aim to
                    address these challenges. Reducing food wastage can enhance food security, minimize economic losses,
                    and benefit farmers.</p>
                <b>video source: </b><a target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none;"
                    href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q8sql0U7IQg">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q8sql0U7IQg</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Government Schemes Card -->
            <div class="card" id="govt-schemes-card">
                <h3>Government Schemes for Farmers</h3>
                <div class="slider-container">
                    <div class="slider">
                        <img src="https://static.vikaspedia.in/media/images_en/agriculture/agri-insurance/pmfby.jpg"
                            alt="PMFBY">
                        <img src="https://www.thetechnicalvoice.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/PM-Kisan-Samman-Nidhi-Yojana-Registration-scaled.jpeg"
                            alt="PM Kisan">
                        <img src="https://tnpds.org.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Soil-Health-Card-Scheme-pib-1200x675.jpg"
                            alt="Soil Health Card">
                    </div>
                </div> <br><br>
                <p><b>Discover various government schemes available to farmers to support them in farming and financial
                        stability.</b></p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana (PMFBY):</strong> Crop insurance scheme providing risk
                        coverage against natural calamities.</li>
                    <li><strong>PM Kisan Samman Nidhi Yojana:</strong> Direct income support to farmers, offering â‚¹6,000
                        per year in three installments.</li>
                    <li><strong>Soil Health Management (SHM):</strong> Aims to improve soil health through awareness and
                        subsidies for soil testing.</li>
                </ul><br>
                <B>Video source: </B><a style="text-decoration: none;" target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UhZAgYPXmCk">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UhZAgYPXmCk</a>
            </div>
            <!-- New Agricultural Products Card -->
            <div class="card" id="new-products-card">
                <h3>New Agricultural Products</h3>
                <div class="slider-container">
                    <div class="slider">
                        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRnCD1ZdZHvb7U3TmOw_Fpb6nnSj-K6ZAPsQw&s" alt="Tractors">
                        <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSq9h5qaMYxdpJbYDghdANCAn-lYRrdiKpSyri6_-d3rca3HUyj1ML8fE6asjHptpIhiT8&usqp=CAU"
                            alt="Innovative Farming Tools">
                    </div>
                </div><br>
                <p><b>Get to know about the latest innovations like new tractor models and advanced farming tools.</b></p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Tractors:</strong> New models like Mahindra Yuvo 275 DI, offering advanced features like
                        fuel efficiency and comfort, are revolutionizing farming practices in India.</li>
                    <li><strong>Innovative Agricultural Products:</strong> Farmers can now access high-efficiency
                        sprayers and automated irrigation systems that save water and improve crop yield.</li>
                </ul><br>
                <b>video source: </b><a style="text-decoration: none;" target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ry9rnbsm_zc">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ry9rnbsm_zc</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Crop Insurance Awareness Card -->
            <div class="card" id="crop-insurance-card">
                <h3>Crop Insurance Awareness</h3>
                <div class="slider-container">
                    <div class="slider">
                        <img src="https://www.mahitisiri.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Crop-Insurance-Karnataka.webp" alt="Crop Insurance">
                    </div>
                </div><br>
                <p><b>Learn about the crop insurance options that help secure farmers' livelihoods in case of unexpected weather events.</b></p>
                <p>Crop insurance awareness is crucial for protecting farmers against financial losses due to unpredictable weather and natural calamities. Schemes like the "Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana (PMFBY)" offer comprehensive coverage for crop damage. Despite its benefits, awareness and enrollment remain low in some regions due to lack of information and accessibility. Increased outreach and simplified claim processes are vital to encourage adoption. Crop insurance not only secures farmers' livelihoods but also fosters confidence to invest in modern agricultural practices.</p>
                <br>
                <b>video source: </b><a style="text-decoration: none;" target="_blank" href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLdCUBRkwWUfrXxz_hCWktp9Va_hMxqP6j">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLdCUBRkwWUfrXxz_hCWktp9Va_hMxqP6j</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#" target="_blank">Facebook</a>
                <a href="#" target="_blank">Twitter</a>
                <a href="#" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
            </div>
            <p>Farmers hub &COPY;2025</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Slider functionality
        const sliders = document.querySelectorAll('.slider');

        sliders.forEach(slider => {
            let index = 0;
            const images = slider.querySelectorAll('img');
            const totalImages = images.length;

            function moveSlider() {
                index++;
                if (index >= totalImages) {
                    index = 0;
                }
                slider.style.transform = `translateX(-${index * 100}%)`;
            }

            setInterval(moveSlider, 3000); // Change image every 3 seconds
        });

        // Smooth scroll to top functionality
        const backToTopButton = document.querySelector('.back-to-top');

        backToTopButton.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
            event.preventDefault();
            window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>
